I may not be as eloquent as other reviewers but I can tell you that for me this is one of the absolute best shows on television I have ever seen...

The story is based around two brothers and their quest to uncover and destroy evil entities and ultimately find and destroy a demon that killed their mother. There is alot mystery around why the demon did in fact kill their mother and as the story progresses various clues appear in their adventures which expose a greater plot. The dialogue and acting is superb. The stories themselves are for the most part interesting and full of intriguing plot twists which really make you think. In addition, having the muscle car (67 Chevy Impala) and the classic rock clips are just icing on the cake and fit in with the storyline and its characters perfectly. The show isn't as cotton candy as other shows in its genre and there are definitely darker overtones in the show compared to others. This is one of the many factors that gives the show its charm and make it so enveloping.

I can't imagine anyone watching this show and not getting hooked. Do yourself a HUGE favor and give this show a look. You won't be dissapointed.